snippet.title: Medieval Total War: Viking Invasion 3v3 online part 1/2
snippet.description: Replay of an online game from may 2009. There are still some players enjoying this excellent strategy game every weekend. Comparing with all the other Total War games this one still stands out as most playable, balanced, tactically interesting.
